{"id": "art-589", "label": "Art. 589", "title": "Art. 589: Cazurile de amânare", "slug": "art-589", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_855653463\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1086\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_855653463\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 589:\nCazurile de amânare </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_554915164\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1085\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_554915164\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Executarea\npedepsei închisorii sau a deten&#355;iunii pe via&#355;&#259; poate fi\namânat&#259; în urm&#259;toarele cazuri:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_896498387\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1084\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_896498387\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)când se constat&#259;, pe baza unei expertize\nmedico-legale, c&#259; persoana condamnat&#259; sufer&#259; de o boal&#259;\ncare nu poate fi tratat&#259; în re&#355;eaua sanitar&#259; a\nAdministra&#355;iei Na&#355;ionale a Penitenciarelor &#351;i care face\nimposibil&#259; executarea imediat&#259; a pedepsei, dac&#259; specificul bolii\nnu permite tratarea acesteia cu asigurarea pazei permanente în re&#355;eaua\nsanitar&#259; a Ministerului S&#259;n&#259;t&#259;&#355;ii &#351;i dac&#259;\ninstan&#355;a apreciaz&#259; c&#259; amânarea execut&#259;rii &#351;i\nl&#259;sarea în libertate nu prezint&#259; un pericol pentru ordinea\npublic&#259;. În aceast&#259; situa&#355;ie, executarea pedepsei se amân&#259;\npentru o durat&#259; determinat&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_571829681\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1083\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_571829681\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)când persoana condamnat&#259; este gravid&#259; sau are\nun copil mai mic de un an. În aceste cazuri, executarea pedepsei se amân&#259;\npân&#259; la încetarea cauzei care a determinat amânarea.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1202853063\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1082\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1202853063\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)În cazul prev&#259;zut la alin. (1) lit. a), amânarea\nexecut&#259;rii pedepsei nu poate fi dispus&#259; dac&#259; cel condamnat\n&#351;i-a provocat singur starea de boal&#259;, prin refuzul tratamentului\nmedical, al interven&#355;iei chirurgicale, prin ac&#355;iuni de autoagresiune\nsau prin alte ac&#355;iuni v&#259;t&#259;m&#259;toare, sau în situa&#355;ia în\ncare se sustrage efectu&#259;rii expertizei medico-legale.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1671122902\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1081\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1671122902\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Cererea de amânare a execut&#259;rii pedepsei închisorii\nsau a deten&#355;iunii pe via&#355;&#259; poate fi f&#259;cut&#259; de procuror\n&#351;i de condamnat.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_772338622\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1080\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_772338622\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Cererea poate fi retras&#259; de persoana care a\nformulat-o.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1337357347\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1079\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1337357347\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)Hot&#259;rârile prin care se dispune amânarea\nexecut&#259;rii pedepsei sunt executorii de la data pronun&#355;&#259;rii.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_799084890\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1078\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_799084890\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(6)În cazul în care în timpul amân&#259;rii execut&#259;rii\npedepsei pe numele condamnatului este emis un alt mandat de executare a\npedepsei închisorii, acesta nu poate fi executat pân&#259; la expirarea\ntermenului de amânare stabilit de instan&#355;&#259; sau, dup&#259; caz,\npân&#259; la încetarea cauzei care a determinat amânarea.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1216068883\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1077\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1216068883\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(7)Hot&#259;rârea prin care instan&#355;a se\npronun&#355;&#259; asupra cererii de amânare a execut&#259;rii pedepsei poate\nfi atacat&#259; cu contesta&#355;ie la instan&#355;a ierarhic superioar&#259;,\nîn termen de 3 zile de la comunicare.</span></p>"}